thread.title: Clark James Mitchell
thread.title_full: Ticketbis evaluado por Clark James Mitchell

author: Clark James Mitchell
title: Clark James Mitchell
text:
Provided the tickets I wanted cheaper than any other resale sites two weeks before the match. In fact they were still cheaper than the other ones on the day of the match.
If I am looking for sold out tickets again I would have no problem using this site again and as such can happily provide a personal recommendation to other users
